        "created_at": "2024-12-06T17:09:33.836Z",
        "cooked": "<p><strong>Dear Signal Developers, (best app so far ;))</strong><br>\nCan we add (I hope) some two features?</p>\n<ol>\n<li>\n<p>I would like to know that someone wrote to me by flashing/bouncing/whatever icon -  to let user know that somewhere under dozens of windows, there are Signal unread messages that needs attention.</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>Could Signal also indicate in small circle number of unread messages? (this is not mandatory, 1st point is crucial).</p>\n</li>\n</ol>\n<p><strong>Thank you in advance.</strong></p>",
